description: JuniorData is the easy-to-learn, easy-to-use data access framework for .NET. This package provides data access components for PostgreSQL.

ImageProcessor.Web adds a configurable HttpModule to your website which allows on-the-fly processing of image files. The module also comes with a file and browser based cache that can handle up to 12,960,000 images increasing your processing output and saving precious server memory.

Methods include; Resize, Rotate, Flip, Crop, Watermark, Filter, Saturation, Brightness, Contrast, Quality, Format, Vignette, and Transparency.

This package also requires Microsoft.Bcl.Async -pre which will be added in the background on install.

If you use ImageProcessor please get in touch on my twitter @james_m_south


Feedback is always welcome.
summary: An extension to ImageProcessor that allows on-the-fly processing of image files in an ASP.NET website
